{"tid":1780671,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"40歲蕭亞軒啜爆24歲男友放閃","createTime":"2019-12-12T14:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T18:54:57.000Z","uid":215823,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2272648d443e25f56b2b83f55ff75e0d03cfe4","tid":1780671,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:17:07.000Z","msg":"40歲台灣天后蕭亞軒（Elva）戀上細16年的小鮮肉男友黃皓，Elva還搵男友為新歌《當你和心跳一起出現》拍MV，兩人在MV裏面甜蜜咀嘴，還在床上親密依偎放閃，充滿激情。<br />\n<br />\n當Elva提出合作拍MV時，男友立刻答應，Elva說：「我們沒有溝通很久，因為一直是朝同一個方向去努力的，會有這一切都是因為有愛。我也跟他說，這將會在我們的生命中留下一個很美好的印記。不管未來會怎麼樣，至少我們現在是同步呼吸、同個節奏。我也告訴他『你不排斥，我就會很勇敢地去做』。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2stsyGZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2stsyGZ.jpg&h=2cfd8560&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbb84b385ffc61f773c73a65ef866aefc52c801e","tid":1780671,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e714b0532a2293b0227c9bfec627db6cce9fae","tid":1780671,"uid":24570,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:22:14.000Z","msg":"16碎，做得佢個仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7748fcf27024730a57fb4d957a3a560ef6cbe5","tid":1780671,"uid":54121,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:22:35.000Z","msg":"呢件老妖都唔知係唔係練開採陰補陽之術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64c7aba5983020b695313d52b615161a204e360","tid":1780671,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"唔知我40歲食唔食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b08bb93910e7f335933b896647987a4c4b7f39b","tid":1780671,"uid":185651,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2f7748fcf27024730a57fb4d957a3a560ef6cbe5","tid":1780671,"uid":54121,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-